<plot>Using found footage, outtakes from an old documentary about North African nomads the film unfolds as a radical critique of ethnographic filmmaking. The film brings together personal narrative, literary references and theoretical commentary to provoke a confrontation with the accepted narrative authority and alleged neutral, documentary gaze.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?616753</url></doc>
